text: the 2016 Kuwait Super Cup was between league champions Qadsia SC and Emir cup champions Kuwait SC. This was the first super cup held in Jaber Al-Ahmad International Stadium. Kuwait SC won 3-2 on penalties. ==References== ==External links== *Kuwait League Fixtures and Results at FIFA *Kuwaiti Super Cup (Arabic) *xscores.com Kuwait *goalzz.com - Super Cup *RSSSF.com - Kuwait - List of Champions Category:Kuwait Premier League seasons Super Cup
